{
  "texts": [
    "• Communicating with stakeholders: Reports, presentations, and",
    "other documents developed with the help of LLMs may be shared with relevant parties such as scientists, doctors, and regulators.",
    "These models may help make decisions and answer questions from interested parties.",
    "• Repurposing existing drugs: LLMs may be used to locate existing therapies that might be repurposed for new uses by analyzing the chemical structure of pharmaceuticals and finding potential new targets for commercially hit drugs.",
    "• Interpreting clinical trial data: Using data from clinical trials, LLMs may be used to make hypotheses about the underlying mechanisms of action, assess the efficacy of existing drugs, and identify potential new therapeutic targets."
  ]
}